Name: RUKUS - January 2014
Format: PDF

RUKUS magazine March 2013 issue with cover model Magda Angel. The featured girls are Jennifer Gonzales and Jamie Centers. Albums reviewed for this issue are Ben Harper and Charlie Musselwhite; Get Up! and Gucci Mane; God Trap 2. Album Spotlight reviews are Buckcherry, Atlas Genius and Tim Chaisson. Concert review is Tegan and Sara. The games reviewed are Aliens: Colonial Marines and Dead Space 3.
